            </div>
            <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-200 to-transparent"></div>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Project Management</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Poor project management leads to missed deadlines, inflated budgets, and stalled innovation. An outside perspective provides the clarity and strategic insights needed to transform inefficiency into streamlined success. I don't believe in one-size-fits-all — I draw from Agile, Scrum, Lean, and traditional frameworks to craft something that fits you.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Focus areas:</span> Process optimization, tool implementation, team alignment, workflow design</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Divider -->
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6"><div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-brand-200 to-transparent"></div></div>

  <!-- Community Development -->
  <section class="py-20 scroll-reveal">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="slide-in-left">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500 to-brand-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-brand-200">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-200 to-transparent"></div>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Community Development</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Building and nurturing a strong community is crucial for sustainable success. Being deeply involved in operations makes it hard to see the broader picture. I help you view your community efforts objectively — uncovering opportunities and potential pitfalls. This isn't about increasing numbers; it's about fostering genuine connections and a sense of belonging.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Focus areas:</span> Community strategy, engagement frameworks, culture building, leadership development</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide-in-right bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-brand-50/40 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-brand-100/60 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-500">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">My Approach</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            {[
              { step: '01', title: 'Community Audit', desc: 'Assess your current community health, engagement patterns, and growth potential.' },
              { step: '02', title: 'Engagement Framework', desc: 'Design rituals, touchpoints, and systems that keep members active and invested.' },
              { step: '03', title: 'Leadership Development', desc: 'Identify and empower community champions who can scale your impact.' },
              { step: '04', title: 'Metrics & Tracking', desc: 'Define what success looks like and build dashboards to measure it.' },
            ].map((item) => (
              <div class="flex gap-4 group">
                <span class="text-brand-600 font-bold text-sm mt-1 opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">{item.step}</span>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">{item.title}</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">{item.desc}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Divider -->
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6"><div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-brand-200 to-transparent"></div></div>

  <!-- Brand Positioning -->
  <section class="py-20 scroll-reveal">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1 slide-in-left bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-500">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">My Approach</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            {[
              { step: '01', title: 'Brand Audit', desc: 'Evaluate how your brand is truly perceived — visual identity, messaging, and market positioning.' },
              { step: '02', title: 'Positioning Workshop', desc: 'Collaborative sessions to define who you are, who you serve, and why it matters.' },
              { step: '03', title: 'Messaging Framework', desc: 'Clear, consistent language that resonates with your audience across every channel.' },
              { step: '04', title: 'Implementation Support', desc: 'Hands-on guidance to roll out your refreshed brand with confidence.' },
            ].map((item) => (
              <div class="flex gap-4 group">
                <span class="text-brand-600 font-bold text-sm mt-1 opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">{item.step}</span>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">{item.title}</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">{item.desc}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2 slide-in-right">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500 to-brand-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-brand-200">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-200 to-transparent"></div>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Brand Positioning</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Your brand is more than a logo or tagline — it's how your audience perceives and connects with your business. A fresh set of eyes can reveal how your brand is truly perceived in the marketplace, identifying strengths and areas needing improvement. This objective insight keeps your brand relevant, compelling, and aligned with market demands.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Focus areas:</span> Brand identity, digital presence, value proposition, market perception</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Divider -->
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6"><div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-brand-200 to-transparent"></div></div>

  <!-- Personal Mentorship -->
  <section class="py-20 scroll-reveal">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="slide-in-left">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500 to-brand-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-brand-200">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-200 to-transparent"></div>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Personal Mentorship</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Having a mentor is like having a secret weapon. It's not just about avoiding mistakes — it's about making smarter decisions that propel you forward. The right mentor provides insights and perspectives you might not see on your own, helping you unlock creative solutions and innovative approaches to personal and professional challenges.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6">
            <p class="text-gray-600"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Focus areas:</span> Mindset development, strategic thinking, decision-making, personal growth</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide-in-right bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-brand-50/40 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-brand-100/60 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-500">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">My Approach</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            {[
              { step: '01', title: 'Deep Discovery', desc: 'Diving into your world — understanding your dreams, strengths, and the obstacles you face.' },
              { step: '02', title: 'Bespoke Plan', desc: 'Crafting a uniquely tailored roadmap designed just for you — no one-size-fits-all.' },
              { step: '03', title: 'Dynamic Sessions', desc: 'Engaging conversations with honest, unfiltered feedback using creative and practical techniques.' },
              { step: '04', title: 'Empowerment', desc: 'Building your resilience and strategic thinking so you make confident, impactful decisions on your own.' },
            ].map((item) => (
              <div class="flex gap-4 group">
                <span class="text-brand-600 font-bold text-sm mt-1 opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">{item.step}</span>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">{item.title}</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">{item.desc}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
